query.comment: The car cannot be simultaneously driving normally and slowing down.
Is it possible for the car to ever reach the "SlowingDown" state? (Sanity check) \\Should Fail if the scenario is blocked to select [0,0] in both cases
Whenever an ambulance approaches, the car eventually becomes aware of it.
The OBLIGATION property: Whenever an emergency is declared, the Car will slow down
This fails. Not always slows down, only if an emergency is declared
The OPTIONAL property (part 1): Is it possible to be at the decision point and subsequently choose to continue driving normally?
The OPTIONAL property (part 2): Is it possible to be at the decision point and subsequently choose to slow down?

query.formula: strategy SociallyAware = control: A[] (!SO2.Error) under AllCars
